  "name": "Striking Stance Cobra",
  "type": "spell",
  "img": "systems/n5eb/assets/Icons%20%26%20Images/Clans/Hebi.png",
  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You can only gain the benefit from one Striking Stance at a time. <br />If you enter another Striking Stance while currently benefiting from this one, the one immediately ends. <br />You enter the coiling stance of a Cobra. <br />For the duration, weapon and taijutsu attacks made using a component weapon ignores temporary hit points, instead dealing direct damage to the target creature.</p>",
